1
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:04,720
Why do I have to do this?

2
00:02:47,040 --> 00:02:48,120
You're right.

3
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,400
I am Zhu Luoli.

4
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:59,280
This used to be my happy home.

5
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:03,410
Thanks to your brother, Song Huainan,

6
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:09,360
everything has been reduced to rubble.

7
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:12,920
My brother isn't that kind of person.

8
00:03:12,920 --> 00:03:14,840
But the one who led the slaughter of the Zhu family

9
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:16,200
was his adjutant.

10
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:19,000
The person who chased me down

11
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,600
and tried to drown me in the pond,

12
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:21,930
how could I mistake him?

13
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:38,220
These are the scars from my plastic surgery.

14
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:41,579
To seize the Zhu family's assets,

15
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:45,300
Song Huainan and the Yao family conspired to set this trap.

16
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:47,720
I got plastic surgery to look like Yao Shengsheng and returned

17
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:49,780
just to take revenge on Song Huainan.

18
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:53,560
That's impossible. You're lying to me.

19
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:01,180
Justice will prevail.

20
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:04,040
Sooner or later,

21
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:07,410
I will tear off his hypocritical mask.

22
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,040
Zhu Luoli.

23
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:15,650
I won't let you hurt the Song family

24
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:17,000
or my brother.

25
00:04:26,880 --> 00:04:28,210
There's one more thing.

26
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:31,000
If you knew about it,

27
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:34,000
you wouldn't think so.

28
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:42,440
This is the place.

29
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:37,480
Mother.

30
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,320
Qingzhou.

31
00:05:52,960 --> 00:05:53,920
Mother.

32
00:05:55,080 --> 00:05:55,880
Mother.

33
00:05:57,440 --> 00:05:59,300
I thought I'd never see you again.

34
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:00,980
After all these years,

35
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:03,080
I've finally found you.

36
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:07,520
I also thought I'd never see you again in this life.

37
00:06:07,760 --> 00:06:08,320
I...

38
00:06:08,320 --> 00:06:09,450
didn't expect this.

39
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:12,160
You found me after all.

40
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:16,530
Mother, please sit down first.

41
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,720
Can you tell me

42
00:06:22,080 --> 00:06:24,000
why you left without a word back then,

43
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,330
leaving the Song family

44
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,360
and me?

45
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,160
Back then,

46
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:33,240
when Huainan's mother passed away,

47
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:36,680
he hated me to the bone.

48
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:44,600
Huainan, although your mother has passed away,

49
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:45,840
rest assured.

50
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,810
In the future, I will...

51
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,240
Shut up.

52
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:53,200
You killed my mother.

53
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,400
Huainan.

54
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:58,960
My parents were a loving couple.

55
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:02,020
Why did you have to come between them?

56
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:03,520
If it weren't for you,

57
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:07,160
my mother wouldn't have died of a broken heart.

58
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:10,920
You killed my mother.

59
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:13,200
You should pay for it with your life.

60
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:13,960
How dare you!

61
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:17,320
Where did you hear

62
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:19,080
such nonsense?

63
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,860
Why are you still here?

64
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:37,760
Get out!

65
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,200
Huainan,

66
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:40,800
you relied on my father's favoritism

67
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,840
to drive my mother to her death.

68
00:07:41,840 --> 00:07:42,640
Let me tell you,

69
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:44,520
the Song family has no place for someone like you.

70
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:46,880
Huainan, there is a misunderstanding between us.

71
00:07:46,880 --> 00:07:49,720
Between you and Qingzhou, the Song family can only keep one.

72
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,720
Make your choice.

73
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:53,520
Three days. I'll give you three days.

74
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:55,360
If you refuse to leave by then,

75
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:59,340
I don't mind finding someone to send you on your way.

76
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:03,160
I didn't take his words seriously then.

77
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:06,160
Who knew he'd actually send someone to kill me?

78
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:10,200
After escaping death,

79
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:11,800
I decided

80
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:14,290
never to return to the Song family.

81
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:16,400
Because I was afraid.

82
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:23,960
Mother.

83
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:27,080
Afraid of what?

84
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:28,800
I was afraid

85
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,080
that if I returned,

86
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:33,440
he wouldn't even

87
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,320
tolerate you.

88
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:46,480
Qingzhou, where are you going?

89
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:48,640
Mother, sit down first.

90
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:51,040
I'm going to find Song Huainan.

91
00:08:51,040 --> 00:08:53,080
I want to ask him why he treated you like that.

92
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,440
No, Qingzhou.

93
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:56,080
Don't be impulsive.

94
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,080
Mother.

95
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:07,880
Mother.

96
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:14,960
I'll listen to you.

97
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:21,500
Commander.

98
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:42,660
What's with that look?

99
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,320
Are you going to eat me?

100
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:46,440
What?

101
00:09:46,640 --> 00:09:49,640
Are you still angry about what happened this morning?

102
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:51,040
Qingzhou.

103
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:53,320
No matter what misunderstandings you have about me,

104
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,480
you must remember,

105
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:56,640
the only person you can trust

106
00:09:57,040 --> 00:09:58,160
is me.
